OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781923667
OL,3,CHow 'heat dome' is set to break 1976
OL,4,Csummer record with temperatures of 35C
OL,6,FRecord-breaking temperatures are
OL,7,Fforecast for parts of the UK next
OL,8,Fweek, in the second heatwave of the
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FExpect it to be hot and humid with
OL,12,Fwarm stuffy uncomfortable nights.
OL,14,FTo have temperatures close to 35C in
OL,15,Fthe summer is becoming more and more
OL,16,Ffrequent - and to see the heat in May
OL,17,Fof this year, during the spring, was
OL,18,Fexceptional.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
