PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781923667
OL,3,CHow 'heat dome' is set to break 1976
OL,4,Csummer record with temperatures of 35C
OL,6,FThe summer of 1976 is remembered as
OL,7,Fone of the most remarkable heatwaves
OL,8,Fin UK memory, when temperatures
OL,9,Fregularly exceeded 30C across England
OL,10,Fand peaked at 35.9C in Cheltenham,
OL,11,FGloucestershire, on July 3.
OL,13,FWhere is the heat coming from?
OL,15,FEurope is already seeing extreme heat
OL,16,F- with highs close to 40C in Spain and
OL,17,FPortugal, and closer to mid 40s
OL,18,Fexpected next week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
