PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781923667
OL,3,CHow 'heat dome' is set to break 1976
OL,4,Csummer record with temperatures of 35C
OL,6,FThe soil in many regions has been
OL,7,Fexceptionally dry after the May
OL,8,Fheatwave, and the lack of moisture
OL,9,Freduces the Earths natural ability to
OL,10,Fcool itself through evaporation.
OL,12,FThis then exacerbates the heat and
OL,13,Fallows temperatures to soar even
OL,14,Fhigher.
OL,16,FWhat does this mean for the UK?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
