PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781923667
OL,3,CHow 'heat dome' is set to break 1976
OL,4,Csummer record with temperatures of 35C
OL,6,FThe positioning of the heat over
OL,7,FEurope means we will see temperatures
OL,8,Frise quickly in the next few days,
OL,9,Fsurpassing 30C across the south-east
OL,10,Fby Sunday, the summer solstice and
OL,11,Flongest day of the year.
OL,13,FThe UK will therefore see maximum
OL,14,Fsunshine hours with sun at its maximum
OL,15,Fstrength this time of year.
OL,17,FNext week will bring heatwave
OL,18,Fconditions and heat health warnings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
