FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781923667
OL,3,CHow 'heat dome' is set to break 1976
OL,4,Csummer record with temperatures of 35C
OL,6,FThe hot and humid air will bring
OL,7,Fthundery conditions at times, so
OL,8,Fexpect storms to develop from the
OL,9,Fcontinent and move towards us.
OL,11,FThe clouds will sometimes cap
OL,12,Ftemperatures but it will still feel
OL,13,Fvery warm and muggy - almost tropical
OL,14,F- at these times.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
